that you wanted me to stay with you.

48
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,080
I have no way to repay you

49
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,440
for saving my life.

50
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,240
I can only offer myself to you.

51
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,400
Your Majesty,

52
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,000
are you willing to accept me?

53
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,400
I never expected you

54
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,920
to say something like that.

55
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:51,740
♪Fearless, the falling flowers
love the eastern river♪

56
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:54,020
♪All for nothing,
resembling someone we know♪

57
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,840
Your Majesty,

58
